00:15:08.290 --> 00:15:10.790
as I said in my introduction,
at the moment there's

00:15:10.790 --> 00:15:14.810
a large study at CERN happening
for a circular collider

00:15:14.810 --> 00:15:15.310
instead.

00:15:15.310 --> 00:15:17.185
So Frank, over to you.

00:15:17.185 --> 00:15:17.685
OK.

00:15:17.685 --> 00:15:19.390
